{"tid":88210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特首選戰】泥頭車撼座駕 胡官偕女兒一額汗","createTime":"2017-01-20T12:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T02:51:44.000Z","uid":53003,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60d74eca9e2a57cd7592c6a7dd2ff80347afa473","tid":88210,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T12:46:53.000Z","msg":"最早宣佈參選特首的退休大法官胡國興晚上遇交通意外，晚上7時許，胡官乘座駕與女兒及一男一女競選辦職員，由司機駕車打算前往私人宴會，座駕途經灣仔皇后大道東近伊利沙伯體育館對出燈位時，右邊一部泥頭車切線駛至，撞及胡官座駕的右邊車身，兩車車身同告損毀。<br />\n<br />\n胡官向《蘋果》記者表示，他坐於車頭乘客位，當時未知是撞車，誤以為座駕「踩到嘢」，感覺成架車被吊起，幸無人受傷。胡官指，受事件影響耽誤了大約半小時，現時仍在場協助警方調查。胡又稱，其座駕損毀須維修，或會影響競選工作，未來幾日可能會搭港鐵出席有關活動，之後胡官便乘的士離開。<br />\n<br />\n讀者余先生事發時剛巧途經上址，見到胡官與同行人士站在路邊向警方交待事件，其間胡官神色凝重，各人都未有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170120&amp;guid=56200959&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170120%26guid%3D56200959%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=79EXsNWsPp3oP0Kg6YFLVksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=d6e9d364\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170120%26guid%3D56200959%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=449a22a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170120&amp;guid=56200959&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"92f528f543ab2f002594357447d4c6322548fc06","tid":88210,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T12:49:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de22c3784dd72265f7c5787302a52f3c794dcd04","tid":88210,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T12:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13020e040f16e66eb084a662e9fe107d00